{"tid":1210064,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"好慚愧留唔到最後","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T23:29:37.000Z","uid":6578,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f40a0bc81638d02566413d05d0f11c9f2575206f","tid":1210064,"uid":6578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"作為動物台嘅敗類我今日都一路衝上前<br />\n食咗我已經唔知幾多10粒催淚彈<br />\n全新手手腳腳都選晒流晒血<br />\n但係因為催淚彈嘅化學成份引起我本身被敏感同埋皮膚敏感嘅症狀嚴重得好犀利<br />\n你朋友要求我撤退返屋企<br />\n<br />\n對唔住咁多位我只係一個夜晚留守到下晝敗走灣仔嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n我真係好慚愧<br />\n因為動物台係睇日本嘅動畫起家<br />\n<br />\n我居然連佢哋逆境正面嘅勇氣<br />\n到而家都學唔到對唔住"},{"pid":"c92943269da0d81635b4d5be759c3caa78ef5033","tid":1210064,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a857ea5133fdd3d506189bb517b7af22150ccc96","tid":1210064,"uid":36300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"唔慚愧"},{"pid":"1f6896ebe7cd376d7e6b738c1038202310472ef9","tid":1210064,"uid":6578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"全身又痕又痛又反胃隻眼好似被火燒緊咁<br />\n<br />\n唉 如果我強壯啲就好"},{"pid":"1d43b49cba6d7d7990aa6ab4641926edf627f115","tid":1210064,"uid":39181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"你已經好勇敢"},{"pid":"bbf2e977342a5c8779adf4a47fb57ee5520925d2","tid":1210064,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"今日我地已經輸左 一定要退<br />\n再打只係比d警犬發洩"},{"pid":"31544fc3087a14ea2120a9bc72e164561888a762","tid":1210064,"uid":41855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"[長期抗戰] 面對殺人政權，我們可以做的非暴力不合作運動<br />\n既然政府完全唔聆聽我們的訴求，我哋又硬碰唔過盲目的政權走狗，我哋又要轉入長期抗戰，社區工作，非暴力不合作運動。<br />\n<br />\n1. 杯葛TVB - 即刻將屋企部電視，全面取消TVB台，有錢的訂閱有線新聞，有錢的都唔好理佢，最多教返父母去youtube煲劇，都有平衡資訊<br />\n簡單教你如何刪除不必要的電視頻道︰<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/02/23/hkppl-remove-j5-guide/top-news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F02%2F23%2Fhkppl-remove-j5-guide%2Ftop-news%2F&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=b33b0e23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/02/23/hkppl-remove-j5-guide/top-news/</a><br />\nCredit to: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1204207/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1204207/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2.  以十多人至數十人為單位於城市各處自發堵路，在警察執法時配合離去（過冷河後可以去附近重新堵路）<br />\n用合理速度不斷橫過行人優先的班馬線，或在守法情況下以安全速度橫過交通燈即可（在香港，15米內沒有合適過路設施，中間又沒有欄杆路障，就可以直接橫過馬路）<br />\n喜歡踩單車的人，也可以在馬路上合法騎行，只要保持單行（但可以佔據一條行車線保障自己安全），而且入黑後配有頭燈尾燈即可。<br />\n路上有不少死火或違泊車輛，而死火當然不犯法，違泊也非刑事。<br />\n乘客搭地鐵也有權力及理由在月台靜候舒適和有空位可坐的列車。<br />\n亞美尼亞「天鵝絨革命」成功背後的抗爭行為︰<a href=\"https://aukalun.blogspot.com/2019/02/blog-post.html?fbclid=IwAR28j5eHXW9wAvcllQwctj4LRTx4yRVuH386JrNTANbSRef1uVG_kyeEgTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faukalun.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F02%2Fblog-post.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR28j5eHXW9wAvcllQwctj4LRTx4yRVuH386JrNTANbSRef1uVG_kyeEgTE&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=5e06a3c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aukalun.blogspot.com/2019/02/blog-post.html?fbclid=IwAR28j5eHXW9wAvcllQwctj4LRTx4yRVuH386JrNTANbSRef1uVG_kyeEgTE</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 100萬市民，全面抵抗建制派的店舖<br />\n我哋有一百萬個市民，全面抵制務求佢哋少 1/7 的生意<br />\n以下呢個表，係建制陣型，我哋以後唔好再幫襯，第一頁係已知的(邀請有心人做admin一齊核實)，第二頁係俾大家舉報而未經核實的。<br />\n如果有IT 朋友，可以整個搜尋APP俾人下載，等香港大眾幫襯前搜一搜，咁就好幫到手了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wBqeOlGpJnW1igj6w2uhOXGCtiz202fDRrl9WRvB76w/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1wBqeOlGpJnW1igj6w2uhOXGCtiz202fDRrl9WRvB76w%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=ce95b5f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wBqeOlGpJnW1igj6w2uhOXGCtiz202fDRrl9WRvB76w/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 抗稅 - 佢老母，交稅俾警察升裝備打自己，點解我要咁撚蠢。<br />\n捐撚左佢- 「根據香港法例，納稅人可申請從應課薪俸稅入息實額、利得稅應評稅利潤或個人入息課稅入息總額中，扣除捐贈給獲豁免繳稅的慈善團體的捐款，總額不得少於$100，也不得超過在該年度的入息減去可扣除支出及折舊免稅額後或應評稅利潤的35%。」換言之，我們先捐款給心儀的慈善團體，然後合法申請扣稅。雖然總支出會比未捐前高，但政府稅收也會稍為減少，又可以促進民間社會的發展。<br />\n用信用卡轉賬分開交稅 - 「良心抗稅運動」專頁引述網民的估算，指如市民經信用卡交稅，銀行會向政府收取2至4% ，或最少3至5元的手續費 (請有關人士証實)。如市民分拆交稅，有可能政府需支付予銀行的手續費會增加。之後交稅，交1000次$5，政府實收稅就會下降不少。<br />\n公民交稅的教育︰<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/500216/%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%812,000%20%E5%BC%B5%E6%94%AF%E7%A5%A8%E4%BA%A4%E7%A8%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F500216%2F%25E9%25A9%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%25812%2C000%2520%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%2594%25AF%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25A8%2585&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=6863b536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/500216/%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%812,000%20%E5%BC%B5%E6%94%AF%E7%A5%A8%E4%BA%A4%E7%A8%85</a>"},{"pid":"2730dc33f780ecaefcc2cd961ef1d4d4945f8b1c","tid":1210064,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"辛苦了<br />\n手足好多都有去 又要畀人話 好好保重"},{"pid":"50a7818c3f3f7094f4e866c6ff0325c6dcb33dbe","tid":1210064,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf2e977342a5c8779adf4a47fb57ee5520925d2","tid":1210064,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"今日我地已經輸左 一定要退<br />\n再打只係比d警犬發洩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"唔算輸 今日已經搞到二讀唔到<br />\n已經算係贏左"},{"pid":"93edecb9905057915067fde71d641985189c3a45","tid":1210064,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:59:26.000Z","msg":"今日我一邊打飛機一邊睇直播  上下都流淚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GO2uQV6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGO2uQV6.gif&h=e1bef565&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b43f6dc4b5c238f058cf38298735b951de576485","tid":1210064,"uid":6578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:29:37.000Z","msg":"已經休息完 洗晒傷口<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 去藥房買完物資<br />\n我再出嚟同你博命"}]}